PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION assented to by the OLD MASSET VILLAGE COUNCIL BAND OF INDIANS which provides for the surrender, for a term of 30 years, of the whole of Tatense Indian Reserve No. 16 in British Columbia for the purpose of leasing it for the operation of a sports fishing lodge to be operated by a band-owned and operated company.
